<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><meta charset="utf-8"><title>Welcome to CBC Platform</title></head>
<body style="font-family:Arial,sans-serif;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;padding:20px">
  <h2 style="color:#2563eb">Welcome to CBC Platform, {{schoolName}}!</h2>
  <p>Your school account has been successfully created.</p>
  <p><strong>Admin Email:</strong> {{adminEmail}}</p>
  <p><strong>Subscription:</strong> {{tier}}</p>
  <p>Log in to get started:</p>
  <a href="{{loginUrl}}" style="background:#2563eb;color:#fff;padding:10px 20px;text-decoration:none;border-radius:4px">Login Now</a>
  <p style="margin-top:30px;color:#6b7280;font-size:12px">CBC Platform — Empowering Kenyan Schools</p>
</body>
</html>
